This paper involves deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves transfer learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper focuses on training an autonomous agent to learn how to behave in multiple tasks simultaneously, which involves robotics (cs.RO). The testing environment used in the paper is Atari games, which involves computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper uses model compression techniques, which is a subfield of neural networks (cs.NE).
